commit.message:
FIXED: Modifying themes sometimes removed backgrounds

The theme dialog always writes all settings to the theme when saved,
so if the original background image had been deleted it would remove
the image from the theme even though the theme uses a private copy.

FIXED: Unable to update contents of theme background image

Confirm that image contents are the same instead of assuming the
image is unchanged if the path is unchanged when editing a theme.
FIXED: Always incremented number for imported themes

Fixed a typo in pt_BR translation

Fixed a typo where Mostrar was written as MOstrar
FIXED: Unable to paste HTML into web browser
